vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting an R-5(A) Single Family District on property zoned CS Commercial Service District, on the north line of Corregidor Street, east of Carbondale Street
Recommendation of Staff:  Denial
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval
Z201-202(OA)
Note: This item was deferred by the City Council before opening the public hearing on June 23, 2021, and is scheduled for consideration on August 25, 2021
